{"tid":740063,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"HKU BA好多major都要dse英文有5先得，可唔可以用ielts代替？","createTime":"2018-07-12T14:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T08:29:51.000Z","uid":35870,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1b06445fa1c0e8b4b3374e3057147013b15974","tid":740063,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:27:42.000Z","msg":"發現hku ba係咪好多major都要dse有咁上下成績先讀得<br />\n例如英文系要英文5先reg得個intro course,translation要中英都有5先讀得個intro<br />\n<br />\n但係若果開學之後考ielts之後可能sem2或者year2先讀返又得唔得？<br />\nIelts可唔可以用黎waive走個requirement?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係dse無5就無機會翻身無可能揀呢d major?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n若果無可能嘅話，去cu讀英文/translation會唔會好過揀hku ba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhku同cu ba 比較邊個勁d?"},{"pid":"401e5768fb5087c3facda961936e7df70b7b857b","tid":740063,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160c02757bbf3014d876b6eb94613afa3ffb8220","tid":740063,"uid":134779,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"除咗中文系<br />\n港大BA勁啲"},{"pid":"94dbe674fc6feca5e881ccde94d004b0c51cc56f","tid":740063,"uid":134554,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:35:03.000Z","msg":"開學先考就唔叫入學requirement啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90923399ae790655dae6278514945dfaa05f8795","tid":740063,"uid":134779,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:36:44.000Z","msg":"問題直接寫信去faculty問啦<br />\nHKU好特別 入咗之後無人理你<br />\n咩都要自己寫信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見你DSE雞 就幫你搵埋個email啦 arts@hku.hk"},{"pid":"53295d713c67f89cd6cc8224a1a2716356f3f240","tid":740063,"uid":138316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"s